Vegas, Mike Tyson-Henry Tillman and George Foreman-Adilson Rodrigues, will be 
televised by HBO. The coverage begins at 7 p.m. . . . CNN will televise a 
half-hour special, "The Mike Tyson Story," Saturday night at 6. Nick Charles 
and Fred Hickman are the co-hosts. 
</P>
