Tonight at 10 on Prime Ticket, there will be a half-hour special featuring a 
behind-the-scenes look at the NCAA Final Four in Denver. Tom Kelly is the host. 
. . . The 500-mile stock car race at Pocono (Pa.) International Raceway Sunday 
will be televised on pay-per-view at 9 a.m. 
