<HEADLINE>
<P>
ISRAEL HOMELAND FOR SOVIET JEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
American Jews should not be sending enormous sums of money to finance Russian 
Jews and encourage them to move to Israel ("Homeward Bound," June 11). 
</P>
<P>
These people have homes in a country that lost over 20 million of its people 
fighting the Nazis. American Jews should be using their influence and money to 
persuade Israel to negotiate with the Palestinians who are really in need of a 
home. 
</P>
<P>
There will never be peace in the Middle East until all people from that area 
have a homeland. 
</P>
<P>
MARGARET JULIANO 
</P>
<P>
San Diego 
</P>
