AGRICULTURE; USSR -- LABOR; USSR -- WAGES AND SALARIES; STANDARD OF LIVING; 
KIRGHIZIA (USSR) -- RIOTS; MINING -- USSR; MINING -- LABOR RELATIONS; COAL 
MINES 
