recite the Pledge of Allegiance at a Flag Day ceremony Thursday. The day was 
also marked by rites at VFW and American Legion posts. In Washington, a 
proposed constitutional amendment to prohibit desecration of the flag faced an 
uphill fight in Congress. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
