<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA061590-0066 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 233942 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 15, 1990, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 27; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
