graduation from Ventura's De Anza Middle School. ; Photo, Students say goodby, 
left, as a limousine waits outside De Anza Middle School in Ventura. Inside, a 
group of tandem surfers pose for a teacher under an artificial wave. ALAN 
HAGMAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Limousine 
</P>
