<P>
Gibson Research Corp., a personal computer software developer, has broken 
ground for its new headquarters in the Mission Viejo Co.'s Pacific Park II 
development in Aliso Viejo. 
</P>
<P>
The company is expected to move from its current 3,700-square-foot location in 
Laguna Hills to the new 19,000-square-foot building in early 1991. Gibson, 
which currently employs 20 people, anticipates expanding to 40 to 60 employees. 
